value.0: A footsoldier of the Broken Tooth.
These thin leather gloves are several centuries old, but due to their lasting enchantments, they still provide the wearer with greatly improved physical strength.
Wearing gloves is usually just a matter of fashion, since they do not afford any protection unless infused with magic.
This well made bastard sword was crafted during the Interregnum and still functions exceptionally, even though the civil war ended a few years ago.
Bastard swords are also known as hand-and-a-half swords, falling between the longsword and greatsword in length.
This is a hammered iron large shield. It should provide a suitable amount of protection.

Tough hemp fibers are woven together to form a rough, yet rollable mattress.  Often place on the ground to keep the moisture from seeping through.  They usually have a worn, old woolen blanket rolled up inside  to use as a pillow or a cover.  Little comfort is achieved when resting on it, but keeps the user dry and warm enough to get a few hours of sleep and is often preferred to sleeping on the bare ground.
